                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mt-4\"><div class=\"u-font-bold u-mb-3 u-mt-3\">User note:</div><div class=\"u-mb-3 u-mt-3\"><span class=\"u-italic\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">About this chapter:</span> Mechanical systems are a key element of any building. Chapter 28 regulates such systems by linking to the </span><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/imc-2021\">International Mechanical Code</a><sup>\u00ae</sup> <span class=\"u-italic\">and </span><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/ifgc-2021\">International Fuel Gas Code</a><sup>\u00ae</sup>, <span class=\"u-italic\">where details of mechanical system requirements are provided.</span></div></div>",
                        "depth": 0,
